              <ul className="text-muted-foreground space-y-1">
                <li>â€¢ Subject-verb disagreement</li>
                <li>â€¢ Incorrect pronoun usage</li>
                <li>â€¢ Misplaced modifiers</li>
                <li>â€¢ Run-on sentences</li>
              </ul>
